{"tid":955510,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"《紙牌屋》總統回歸？凱文史貝西性侵起訴後的「獨白辯護」","createTime":"2018-12-25T12:52:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-08T21:37:49.000Z","uid":51828,"like":36,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"d5bcc92ca07a12db192de2cfc962d44c74728bcb","tid":955510,"uid":51828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-25T12:52:04.000Z","msg":"「我絕不會為我沒做的事付出代價！」捲入性侵風暴的奧斯卡影帝凱文．史貝西（Kevin Spacey），經過一年多的調查，24日因為强暴猥亵的刑事重罪起訴，確定將於2019年1月7日到麻州南塔克特地方法院出庭應訊。但與此同時，史貝西突然打破沉默，在自己的社群媒體上發表了一段平安夜影片，以其影集代表作《紙牌屋》主角法蘭克．安德伍德的角色現身，一面向觀眾喊話「想念我嗎？」、一面為自己的無辜辯白。隨著短片的公開，事業與人格都跌至谷底的史貝西，又引發了一場危機風暴。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=JZveA-NAIDI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DJZveA-NAIDI&d=EAYqXrIIJPGx4S0IDbeNMhv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=b5f57ce6\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=JZveA-NAIDI</a>"},{"pid":"287f2e89cd27683d593f8f07440547573d49eb6b","tid":955510,"uid":213441,"like":0,"dislike":15,"score":-15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-25T13:01:30.000Z","msg":"死基佬"},{"pid":"4bd307494ac3b0ad2b50fcb00621f51bf51bd11d","tid":955510,"uid":51200,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-25T14:23:00.000Z","msg":"屌你有型到<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8fafcfe08243e4baeaac9b5fb045ec26256346a7","tid":955510,"uid":10757,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-25T14:26:10.000Z","msg":"比佢翻生 翻生 翻生<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7856befef8f993ef37128152a3e6aadd62a1fa4","tid":955510,"uid":49359,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-25T14:27:08.000Z","msg":"荷里活個咸濕監製俾班女星禁制公開